tlp (8)              - apply laptop power saving settings
tlp-rdw (8)          - disable Radio Device Wizard temporarily (until reboot).
tlp-stat (8)         - view power saving status
tlp.service (8)      - Initialize power saving at boot and cleanup upon shutdown


{{{REDSHIFT}}}

redshift -x : reset 
